Company email:
Pleas be advised that all our brands is suitable for vegetarian and vegan diets, except for:
- our wines and wine-based products which may be fined with gelatine;
- Martini bitter which is coloured with E120 (cochineal red, extracted from minuscule insects);
- cream liqueurs which contain dairy ingredients;

All the charcoal we use for filtration and fining is made from wood.

Note: this appears to be a response from the parent company covering all brands, but since gin doesn't have any of the issues above, it looks like it's safe.

